title: RHOBH: Let There Be (Gas)Light
description:
It's part one of the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills season 10 reunion, which means it's time to rev up the gaslighting machine! The question is — who's gaslighting who? We're still Team Denise in this dumb feud. Where do you land?Also, don't forget to watch our video recap here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/41206236

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
